'''遠東山雀'''（{{sn|''Parus minor''}}；{{lang-en|Oriental tit}}），也叫'''日本山雀'''（{{lang-en|Japanese tit}}），為[[山雀屬|山雀屬]]的一員，主要分佈於[[中國大陸|中國大陸]]、[[中南半島|中南半島]]北部、[[朝鮮半島|朝鮮半島]]、[[日本|日本]]和[[俄羅斯遠東地區|俄羅斯遠東地區]]。直到最近，此物種仍被歸類為大山雀（{{sn|''Parus major''}}）的[[亞種|亞種]]，但研究表明這兩種物種在俄羅斯遠東地區共存，沒有混合或頻繁雜交。<ref>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1111/j.1095-8312.2005.00529.x | url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/229514602_The_great_tit_%28Parus_major%29__a_misclassified_ring_species | title = The great tit (''Parus major'') – a misclassified ring species | journal = Biological Journal of the Linnean Society | volume = 86 | issue = 2 | pages = 153 | year = 2005 | last1 = Päckert | first1 = M. | last2 = Martens | first2 = J. | last3 = Eck | first3 = S. | last4 = Nazarenko | first4 = A. A. | last5 = Valchuk | first5 = O. P. | last6 = Petri | first6 = B. | last7 = Veith | first7 = M. | access-date = 2018-08-13 | archive-date = 2018-08-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180828093223/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/229514602_The_great_tit_(Parus_major)__a_misclassified_ring_species | dead-url = no }}</ref>

